The one you missed was a soils report‚Äîthose go in 05_Soils specifically
because they're geotechnical, not structural design.
```

### Principle 9: Collaborative Knowledge Building
**How the skill applies it:**
- Paths include mentoring/teaching modules for experts
- Users can contribute discovered patterns
